    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44696</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊を集めるだけじゃ
ダメだったなんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even after collecting all the Spirits...it was useless...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>力のある術者を探せばいいだけだよ、
ほら、精霊たちも言ってたシ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We'll have enough power after we find the Lord of the Four Elements. The Spirits said so, remember?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、精霊の力を使える人なんて
いないんじゃないのかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But what if we can't find that person and we can't control the Spirits?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45084</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ～っ！　なんでどうして、
そう後ろ向きなんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Damn it! Why are you ALWAYS depressed when things get tough?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今のオレらは外の世界を知ったし
いろんなとこに行けんだぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We have the entire world to search for him. Do you think there's somewhere we can't go?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45304</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それに『なりきり士』だし、
時空戦士とも知り合いになれた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Also, we are Roleplayer and we know the Heroes of Time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45420</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こんなすげーこと続いてんだ、
案外、簡単にいい方法見つかるって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've done awesome things already! This looks like it'll be easy as cake!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururu!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……どうして、そんな楽観的なの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Why are you such a Polly Positive?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_035_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだよ、せっかく励まして
やってんのにそりゃねーだろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What!? Here I am, trying to cheer you up and all you do is answer with negativity...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
